---
const pillars = [
  { icon: '🧬', title: 'Science-First', desc: 'Every recommendation backed by research' },
  { icon: '✨', title: 'Aesthetic Plates', desc: 'Because beautiful food is sustainable food' },
  { icon: '📐', title: 'Structured Systems', desc: 'Meal plans, macros, and prep workflows' },
  { icon: '🌿', title: 'Whole Ingredients', desc: 'Clean, anti-inflammatory, nutrient-dense' },
];
---

<section id="about" class="bg-brand-warm-white py-[100px]">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-7">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Portrait -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 fade-up">
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/inzhu-portrait.png"
            alt="Inzhu - Portrait"
            class="rounded-md aspect-[3/4] object-cover w-full"
          />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-brand-sage text-white py-4 px-6 rounded font-serif text-[14px] tracking-wider">
            Bioengineering Student
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="fade-up">
          <span class="section-label">About</span>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up delay-1">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-[36px] sm:text-[44px] mt-4">
            Where science meets<br />the art of eating well.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up delay-2">
          <p class="body-text mt-7">
            I'm Inzhu - a bioengineering student with an obsession for understanding how
            food works at the molecular level and making that knowledge beautiful, practical, and
            accessible. My approach isn't about restriction. It's about building systems that make
            nourishing your body effortless and aesthetically satisfying.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up delay-3">
          <p class="body-text mt-4">
            Every recipe, guide, and program I create is rooted in nutritional science - from
            macronutrient ratios and glycemic responses to microbiome health and anti-inflammatory
            protocols. I break down the complexity so you can eat with confidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillars grid -->
        <div class="fade-up delay-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-10">
          {pillars.map((p) => (
            <div class="pt-5 border-t border-brand-border">
              <div class="text-[20px] mb-2">{p.icon}</div>
              <div class="font-sans text-[13px] font-semibold text-brand-dark tracking-wide">{p.title}</div>
              <div class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-warm-gray mt-1 leading-relaxed">{p.desc}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
